00:01:20.220 --> 00:01:22.950

the content itself for best results.



19

00:01:22.950 --> 00:01:27.020

Your offer should always be a natural extension of the surrounding content.



20

00:01:27.030 --> 00:01:31.750

In other words, trying to offer something that's relevant to that post in particular.



21

00:01:32.640 --> 00:01:33.540

Here's an easy one.



22

00:01:33.540 --> 00:01:39.120

If you have a core lead magnet that you want to promote to your entire audience, your navigation bar



23

00:01:39.120 --> 00:01:41.590

is prime real estate to do just that.



24

00:01:41.910 --> 00:01:47.510

